reviewText: This movie was pretty good, it wasn't a movie that you can predict it was actually nice to watch
Consequences of ones action  usually hurt many and this movie shows you that you show always be on the watch.

My mouth dropped open during the opening scene to this movie.  Even though the movie description tells you what it is about - from the beginning you are not quite sure what is really going on.  Despite the poor sound quality in some spots and a couple of stereotypes, the plot is compelling and the characters believable.  I have to say that there where enough twists and turns in the plot to keep me interested and things did not turn out the way I expected. I liked it!
